---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Books by Jimmy Pidgeon | From the Streets to the Steps"
  description="Explore 'From the Streets to the Steps: One Day at a Time,' a powerful memoir by Jimmy Pidgeon. Available in paperback and hardcover."
>
  <div class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="fade-in-up">Books</h1>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="books-section section-padding">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="book-card scroll-reveal">
        <div class="book-cover-col">
          <img
            src="/cover.png"
            alt="From the Streets to the Steps"
            class="book-cover"
          />
        </div>

        <div class="book-info-col">
          <h2>From the Streets to the Steps</h2>
          <h3 class="subtitle">One Day at a Time – A Memoir</h3>

          <div class="metadata">
            <p><strong>Author:</strong> Jimmy Pidgeon with Ben Rose</p>
            <p><strong>Publisher:</strong> Oracle Bookart Publishing</p>
            <p><strong>Release Date:</strong> January 6, 2026</p>
            <p><strong>ISBN (Paperback):</strong> 9798349689314</p>
            <p><strong>ISBN (Hardcover):</strong> 9798349689406</p>
          </div>

          <div class="description">
            <p>
              A raw and unflinching memoir chronicling Jimmy's journey from the
              depths of addiction through the transformative power of recovery.
              Part personal story, part guide for anyone seeking a way out, this
              book shows that true change is possible—one day at a time.
            </p>
            <p>
              From the streets where addiction seemed inescapable to the steps
              of sustained recovery and a fulfilling life as a nurse and father,
              Jimmy's story is a profound testament to the human spirit's
              resilience. It's a resource for families, healthcare
              professionals, and anyone who has ever felt that they have
              wandered too far to find their way back home.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="purchase-links">
            <h4>Available at these retailers:</h4>
            <div class="retailer-grid">
              <a
                href="https://a.co/d/05W2aYn4"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="retailer-btn amazon"
              >
                Amazon
              </a>
              <a
                href="https://www.barnesandnoble.com/s/9798349689314"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="retailer-btn bn"
              >
                Barnes & Noble
              </a>
              <a
                href="https://www.target.com/s?searchTerm=9798349689314"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="retailer-btn target"
              >
                Target
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonials scroll-reveal delay-200">
        <h3 class="text-center">What Readers Are Saying</h3>
        <div class="testimonial-grid">
          <div class="testimonial-card">
            <p class="quote">
              "Great story of one man’s continuous journey of sobriety! A must
              for AA and NA , frankly everyone will love the honest, raw
              confessions Jimmy shares as well as the joy and triumphs in his
              life. His analysis and understanding of the program is spot on."
            </p>
            <p class="author">— Laura G, Amazon</p>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial-card">
            <p class="quote">
              "This book isn't just a memoir; it's a lifeline. The 'one day at a
              time' approach is made real on these pages."
            </p>
            <p class="author">— Recovery Community</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      var(--color-primary-dark),
      var(--color-primary)
    );
    color: white;
    padding: calc(80px + var(--space-8)) 0 var(--space-8);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .page-hero h1 {
    color: white;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .section-padding {
    padding: var(--space-16) 0;
    background-color: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .text-center {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }

  .book-card {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    padding: var(--space-8);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
    gap: var(--space-10);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
  }

  .book-cover {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 4px;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }

  .book-info-col h2 {
    color: var(--color-primary-dark);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-1);
    font-size: 2.25rem;
  }

  .subtitle {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  .metadata {
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    padding: var(--space-4);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-2);
  }

  .metadata p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .description {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }

  .purchase-links h4 {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }

  .retailer-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(140px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }

  .retailer-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: var(--space-3);
    text-align: center;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
  }

  .retailer-btn.amazon {
    background-color: #ff9900;
    color: #111;
  }
  .retailer-btn.amazon:hover {
    background-color: #e68a00;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .retailer-btn.bn {
    background-color: #074b39;
    color: white;
  }
  .retailer-btn.bn:hover {
    background-color: #053327;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .retailer-btn.target {
    background-color: #cc0000;
    color: white;
  }
  .retailer-btn.target:hover {
    background-color: #aa0000;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .testimonial-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-6);
  }

  .testimonial-card {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    padding: var(--space-8);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    position: relative;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }

  .quote {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .author {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .book-card {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .book-cover-col {
      max-width: 400px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .metadata {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .testimonial-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
